<br>
My advice would be to get into an ROTC program if you have the desire to join the military.   Another option would be to try to attend one of the military academies (Naval Academy, Air Force Academy, or West Point).  My sister enlisted into the Air Force upon graduating from high school.  She spent 4 years in England, and eventually went into an ROTC program.  She graduated from college and eventually got her Masters in Computer Science.  She is now retired from the Air Force as a Captain.  Her husband, also in the Air Force, is a Captain and currently a pilot.  They don't let them go too easily and still has 3 years left before he can retire.<br>
<br>
The pay in the military is not the greatest, but the oportunities pending your classification are great.  I've known many people that have worked as Intelligence Analysts, Interpretors, and Translators that once they are out of the military get sucked back up by NSA, CIA, DIA, FBI, and many other government work.  Basically, they would leave the military and be back the next week at the same desk as a civilian employee.<br>
<br>
However, I cannot say that those that I know that have been in the Navy have enjoyed it.  Just ask Uenolan or Nonalla.  However, there is one guy I now that was on a submarine that did well - but they're weird to begin with. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub73.ezboard.com/btheprogenysentinels47001.showUserPublicProfile?gid=sentineltaishirmahone>Sentinel Taishir Mahone</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Scrumdiddlyumptious Cavalier of Tunare</span><br>  Posts: 353<br> <font color=#333333>(4/3/03 11:41:37 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub73.ezboard.com/ftheprogenysentinels47001frm52.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=33>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://polaris.umuc.edu/~ehuber/Morgoth_vs_NoldorT.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: OMG!!!!!</span><hr size=1> Mayera,<br>
