<br>
1) ROTC is good. Services academies or military schools are VERY tough. I spent 6 weeks in the Corps of Cadets at Texas A&amp;M, and it was probably the worst 6 weeks of my life. Imagine going through basic training at the same time as your freshman year in college. As a matter of fact, I later went through Air Force enlisted basic training and it was a joke compared to the Corps at A&amp;M. Somem people thrive at the academies, but I'm not one of them.<br>
<br>
2) As far as services: I'd recommend the Air Force if you enlist. I can't speak for officer life, but my life in the Air Force wasn't bad at all. I really enjoyed my time in. Pretty much the only reason I got out was I was bored with my job but didn't want to move somewhere to retrain and get restationed farther from home.  <p><p><table align="center" border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="0" bordercolor=#330000 rules=cols frame=void><tr><td valign=center *****"padding-right: 5px;font-size:9pt"><b><font color=#00008B><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=491922&resize=true target="_blank">Mayera Silverwinds</a><br>52nd Season Wanderer of Tunare</font><br><i>The Progeny Sentinels - Tunare Server</i></br>     <select name = "Tradeskills"><option selected>Tradeskills<option>203 Fletching<option>191 Baking<option>199 Brewing<option>173 Fishing<option>125 Pottery<option>127 Smithing<option>107 Tailoring<option>21 Jewelcraft<br></select>    <a href=http://www.cox-internet.com/silverwinds target="_blank">My EQ Site</a></b></td><td *****"padding-left: 8px"><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=472221&resize=true target="_blank">Darlantan Silverwinds</a> - 24th Season Wood Elf Ranger<br><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=472234&resize=true target="_blank">Avallach Whitewinds</a> - 29th Season Human Warrior<br><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=482894&resize=true target="_blank">Jikshalin</a> - 14th Season Iksar Monk<br><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=472227&resize=true target="_blank"> Dubal</a> - 9th Season Dwarf Cleric<br><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=472331&resize=true target="_blank">Ebriola</a> - 11th Season Gnome Wizard</td></tr><tr><td colspan=2 align=center><hr color=#330000>"The most likely way for the world to be destroyed, most experts agree, is by accident.<br> That's where we come in; we're computer professionals. We cause accidents. - Nath